Logic Samjo, Stock Selection Krna Seekho, Kahi Se Bhi Seekho, Option Trading Pr Km Dhyan Do, jab Moka Ho Tbhi Option Me Work kro, Regular Trading Sirf Equity Swing Trading Me Kre.

Learning Kr Dhyan De, Jyada Gaharayi Me Mat Jao, Simple Stock Selection Krna Seekho, Support Resistance Seekho, RSI Seekho

YouTube Pr Ache Ache Videos Hai Jo Smjh Me Aaye Seekhne ka kosis kro, Company Ka Bio Data Bhi Thoda Dekho Google Pr Sb Hai
P/ E Ratio, ROCE, Market Cap, Margin, Debt
